This will be what CoinBR chairman, Rocelo Lopes will be speaking about at the Blockchain Africa Conference taking place in Johannesburg from 1-3 March 2017. CoinBR is a bitcoin mining and exchange company based in S o Paulo, with remote offices in Singapore and Cape Town, and is the only Brazilian company buying and selling bitcoin without applying administrative fees. The company has come on board as the second official premier sponsor for the conference. Blockchain Africa brings together a diverse range of local and international experts who will discuss all the challenges and exciting possibilities in innovation and disruption that can be leveraged in Africa using this blockchain technology. Buy your ticket for the conference here.